  "texts": [
    "There are several methods to develop these DCT specifications.",
    "These methods differ in terms of, for example, point of departure (e.g., theory, expertise) and number of sources.",
    "We introduce these different methods as well as their benefits and drawbacks.",
    "It is important to keep in mind that these methods are ways to elaborate construct definitions into comprehensive definitions with corresponding instructions -they are not ways to arrive at those constructs.",
    "To that end, we direct readers to procedures to develop theory (e.g., Borsboom et al., 2021; Hawkins-Elder & Ward, 2020; Podsakoff et al., 2016)."
  ],
